title: FBI Leaks Top-Secret Info to Washington Post?
itunes:title: FBI Leaks Top-Secret Info to Washington Post?
description: The FBI has been accused of leaking details about top-secret files supposedly seized in the raid on President Trump's Mar-a-Lago home. Jay, Jordan, and the Sekulow team discuss the latest developments in the case. This and more today on Sekulow.
